<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11153</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20152</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>师徒四人把湿透的卷轴展开铺在岩石上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太阳会晒干卷轴的。”悟空说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27050</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧呻吟了一声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27050</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29768</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真经被毁了的话怎么办？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33624</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他坐下，双手捂住了头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33624</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38170</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真希望我没有忘记问佛祖老龟的问题！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38170</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41377</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒哼了一声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41377</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43998</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谁会在乎那老龟的问题？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43998</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47818</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那只老龟没有权利把我们扔到水里！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47818</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53003</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把我们扔到水里，太无礼了。”悟净同意。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53003</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55869</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒叹了口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55869</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60118</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“回去的路和去西天一样辛苦。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60118</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63368</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们好！”有人喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69868</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>师徒四人回头一看，一个男人在朝他们跑来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69868</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72867</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“老陈。”唐僧说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72867</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76118</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他双手握住了老陈的手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76118</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78618</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很高兴又见到你。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78618</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83368</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也很高兴能再见到你们。”老陈笑了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85867</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们到达西天了吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85867</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90368</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。”唐僧说，“真的棒极了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92618</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那里特别美丽！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92618</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98368</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老陈看见铺在岩石上的卷轴，瞪大了眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102867</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那些是真经吗？”他小声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102867</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105119</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。”唐僧说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105119</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109617</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是，正如你看到的，真经湿了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109617</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116619</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“老龟把我们扔到了河里。”八戒叹了口气说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116619</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120247</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“和我一起走吧。”老陈说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120247</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124335</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们可以把真经晾在我家暖炉旁边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130085</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你们见过佛祖，村里人见到你们都会很高兴的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130085</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134085</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟净开始收拾湿透的真经。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134085</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137085</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我帮你。”八戒说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137085</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141336</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒拿起一个卷轴，向后拉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141336</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146085</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可是，那个卷轴粘到了岩石上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146085</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>刺啦！卷轴一角被撕开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157334</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧吓了一跳。“哦，天啊！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157334</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161335</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒吓得看着撕破的真经。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165835</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空笑了。“别担心，师父。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171084</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空小心地从岩石上捡起被撕坏的部分。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171084</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173345</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“卷轴没事。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173345</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178418</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可是，卷轴被撕开了！”唐僧大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178418</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182168</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒低下了头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182168</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你说说看，师父。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188169</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你很完美吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188169</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193167</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧疑惑地看着悟空。“当然不。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193167</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196273</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我完美吗？”悟空问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196273</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧摇了摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204735</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“八戒怎么样？”悟空咯咯地笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们都知道他不完美。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207235</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210484</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒哼了一声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210484</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215515</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“天上、人间都没有完美的东西。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215515</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219553</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那么，真经又有什么不同呢？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219553</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225599</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>真经会教导东土大唐的人向善，怎么才能避开痛苦。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225599</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234404</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它还会教导人们什么都没有必要变得完美。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234404</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>师徒四人整理好了卷轴，跟着老陈回到了村子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247902</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>人们都从家里出来看他们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247902</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252651</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“欢迎你们回来！”一个女人喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252651</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258653</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很高兴能再次见到你们。”一个老人大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266152</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不一会儿，很多人都跟着唐僧一行人去了老陈的家。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那天晚上，村里人举行盛宴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270717</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>深夜，悟空和唐僧坐着聊天。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>281217</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们得马上走。”唐僧说，“村里人会想看真经，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>281217</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>284220</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>会嫉妒我们拿着真经。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>284220</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287467</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也同意。”悟空说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287467</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>292969</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他记得想要杀死唐僧、偷袈裟的住持。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>292969</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>298719</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在村里人睡着了，我们悄悄地离开这里吧。”悟空说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>298719</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>303218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧和悟空叫醒了八戒和悟净。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>303218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>309968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>师徒四人从老陈的家里悄悄地出来，朝东边走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>309968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>314969</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>天很黑，但是满月把路照得很亮。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>314969</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>319306</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，雷音寺的门将出现了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>319306</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>322852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“祝贺你们！”门将说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>322852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>327101</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们已经经历了九九八十一难。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>327101</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>331306</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“咻。”唐僧安心地吐了口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>331306</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>334117</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我终于能成佛了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>334117</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>336868</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>门将念了一个咒语。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>336868</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>341618</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>师徒四人又朝东边飞去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>